title: Power Outage Analysis
description: To learn more about electrical infrastructure I analyzed major power outages from 2000 to 2016. I performed EDA, extracted and engineered features, and predicted the outage durations using regression and random forests.

title: Alphabet Inc. Stock Analysis
description: I analyzed Alphabet to understand why its stock was priced with a significantly lower P/E than its peers. Using public financial statements I forecasted Alphabetâ€™s value using peer group and historical-based approaches.
